  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and saut\u00143e until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add the cumin, cinnamon, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the beef render fat and stir to combine.",
    "Add the boiled and mashed potatoes and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chopped scallions and stir to combine.",
    "Slice the rocoto peppers in half and fill each pepper with the beef and potato mixture.",
